Package com.cs.pausis.models

Class Summary
AFC This model software representation was created based on the model developed by Marca A.
AMH This model software representation was created based on the model developed by Kelsey et al This class facilitates the calculation of the AMH results based on the statistical model by Kelsey et al 2011 Article can be accessed at: http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?artid=3137624&tool=pmcentrez&rendertype=abstract
BMI This class is for handling the body mass index calculations
DB This class instantiates the main SQLlite database which is used for storing the user data and all the statistical model values.
DB.OpenHelper This is a helper class that facilitates the creation/upgrade of the database tables.
FSH This class facilitates the calculation of the FSH results Article can be accessed at:
MenuItem This is a model class for the menu items
MMAge This class is for handling the Mother's age of Menopause statistical calculations
Months This class models the calendar months of the year, which is used in the application for populating lists
NGF This class facilitates the calculation of the NGF based on the input age
OvarianVolume This model software representation was created based on the model developed by Kelsey et al This class facilitates the calculation of the Ovarian volume results based on the statistical model by Kelsey et al 2011 Article can be accessed at: http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20111701
Result This is the main model class for all the results generated from the different models, all the results are kept in this model so as to allow for consistency in the presentation.
Tracker This is the main model class mainly used for tracking generic indicators within the app such as storing the record of user's privacy policy agreement, it is a direct one-to-one mapping of the corresponding database table(TABLE_TRACKER).
UserInputValues This is the main model class for all the usage history generated throughout the lifetime of the the application, it is a direct one-to-one mapping of the corresponding database table(TABLE_USAGE).
Years This class models the acceptable years of birth (from 1990-1959), which is used in the application for populating lists.
 

Enum Summary
Result.Status This is an enumeration of all the different statuses that result objects can have
Result.Type This is an enumeration of all the different types of result
